{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-medium\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-medium\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-medium</h1>\n<p>Source plugin for pulling data into Gatsby from an unofficial Medium JSON\nendpoint. Unfortunately the JSON endpoint does not provide the complete stories,\nbut only previews. If you need the complete stories, you might have a look at\nsomething like\n<a href=\"https://github.com/jondubin/gatsby-source-rss\">gatsby-source-rss</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-source-medium</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-source-medium`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      username<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`username/publication`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h6 id=\"note\"><a href=\"#note\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Note</h6>\n<p>Remember that if you are fetching a user, prepend your username with <code class=\"language-text\">@</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query\"><a href=\"#how-to-query\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query</h2>\n<p>Get all posts with the preview image ID and the author’s name:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allMediumPost<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">sort</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fields</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>createdAt<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">order</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> DESC <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id\n        title\n        virtuals <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          subtitle\n          previewImage <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            imageId\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        author <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          name\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Get all users with their posts:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">query</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allMediumUser <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        name\n        posts <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          title\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","excerpt":"gatsby-source-medium Source plugin for pulling data into Gatsby from an unofficial Medium JSON\nendpoint. Unfortunately the JSON endpoint…","timeToRead":1,"fields":{"title":"gatsby-source-medium"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"gatsby-source-medium/README.md"}},"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-medium","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"kylemathews","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e567aa8adbd2d49cd9990ea1ed19d4eb"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-medium/","id":"4fa5d461-de56-534a-bd4a-43908bc2ad41"}}